Clarisse Uwineza n'umunyarwandakazi,umuvugabutumwa akaba n'[[Umubyeyi Sharifa|umubyeyi]] wabana babiri, uyu mugore  kandi numunyamakuru ukorera [[Ikigo gishinzwe iterambere mu Rwanda|ikigo]] cy'igihugu cyitangaza makuru (RBA) ukunzwe nabatari bake hano murwanda<ref>https://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/sinema/article/yarwaye-covid-19-inshuro-ebyiri-na-kanseri-ibyo-utamenye-ku-buzima-bwa-uwineza</ref> .

== Umwuga ==
Uwineza amaze  [[imyaka]] irenga 17 yinyiye mumwuga witangazamakuru akaba yaranaryize  muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|kaminuza]]  y'ishuri gatolika rya kabgayi (ICK).Yatangiriye akazi kuri Radio Maria [[Rwanda]] yahamaze imyaka irindwi ahavuye ajya gukorera kuri [[Radio Studio 54 Network|Radio]] salus iherereye mucyahoze ari Butare naho yahamaze imyaka ibiriri ahavuye nibwo yaje  gukorera [[Radio Studio 54 Network|Radio]] Rwanda kuva (2010)<ref>https://nkundagospel.rw/2022/02/23/byinshi-kuri-clarisse-uwineza-umunyamakuru-akaba-numukristu/</ref> kugera ubungubu Clarisse yumvikana mubiganiro bitandukanye birimo "kazi ni kazi na ntarungu" ntaruru  nikiganiro gikunzwe na benshii aho yibanda kukwigisha k'urukundo ndetse no gususutsa abantu mumasaha y'ijoro.

